(8, 'Kdo jsem', '<div class="row">\r\n<div class="col-md-4">\r\n<div class="owl-carousel owl-theme" data-plugin-options="{&quot;items&quot;: 1, &quot;margin&quot;: 10}">\r\n<div><span class="img-thumbnail"> <img class="img-responsive" src="/adminclanek/img/team/team-3.jpg" alt="" height="300" /> </span></div>\r\n<div><span class="img-thumbnail"> <img class="img-responsive" src="/adminclanek/img/team/team-9.jpg" alt="" height="300" /> </span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-md-8">\r\n<h2 class="mb-none">Bc. Ctibor <strong>Venus</strong></h2>\r\n<h4 class="heading-primary">servisn&iacute; technik IT, program&aacute;tor</h4>\r\n<hr class="solid" />\r\n<p>V oblasti IT se pohybuji již od sv&yacute;ch 8 let. Zač&iacute;nal jsem na ZX Spectru, kde jsem si již programoval sv&eacute; prvn&iacute; hry. Sv&eacute; zku&scaron;enosti jsem zužitkoval na univerzitě UP Olomouc, kde jsem &uacute;spě&scaron;ně složil bakal&aacute;řskou skoužku. Po studiu jsem se nejdř&iacute;ve živil jako program&aacute;tor, po civiln&iacute; službě potom jsem k tomu přidal i profesi spr&aacute;vce poč&iacute;tačov&eacute; s&iacute;tě ve velk&eacute; organizaci s v&iacute;ce jak 200 PC stanicemi. Za v&iacute;ce jak 25 let sv&eacute; praxe jsem se naučil, že je nutno se učit st&aacute;le nov&eacute; a nov&eacute; věci a neustrnout na m&iacute;stě. Proto nyn&iacute; sv&eacute; znalosti a dovednosti chci nab&iacute;zet jako drobn&yacute; živnostn&iacute;k.</p>\r\n<h2>Nab&iacute;z&iacute;m V&aacute;m tyto služby</h2>\r\n<ul class="list list-icons">\r\n<li><span class="fa fa-check">&nbsp;</span> ve&scaron;ker&yacute; n&aacute;kup a servis v&yacute;početn&iacute; techniky u V&aacute;s doma, nebo ve va&scaron;&iacute; organizaci.</li>\r\n<li><span class="fa fa-check">&nbsp;</span> tvorba webov&yacute;ch str&aacute;nek.</li>\r\n<li><span class="fa fa-check">&nbsp;</span> programov&aacute;n&iacute; aplikac&iacute; na zak&aacute;zku v PHP, Visual Basic, Access, Excel.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="row">\r\n<div class="col-md-12"><hr /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="row mt-xlg">\r\n<div class="col-md-3">\r\n<div class="circular-bar">\r\n<div class="circular-bar-chart" data-percent="95" data-plugin-options="{&quot;barColor&quot;: &quot;#E36159&quot;}"><strong>IT servis</strong> <label><span class="percent">95</span>%</label></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-md-3">\r\n<div class="circular-bar">\r\n<div class="circular-bar-chart" data-percent="85" data-plugin-options="{&quot;barColor&quot;: &quot;#0088CC&quot;, &quot;delay&quot;: 300}"><strong>PHP</strong> <label><span class="percent">85</span>%</label></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-md-3">\r\n<div class="circular-bar">\r\n<div class="circular-bar-chart" data-percent="60" data-plugin-options="{&quot;barColor&quot;: &quot;#2BAAB1&quot;, &quot;delay&quot;: 600}"><strong>Webdesign</strong> <label><span class="percent">60</span>%</label></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-md-3">\r\n<div class="circular-bar">\r\n<div class="circular-bar-chart" data-percent="85" data-plugin-options="{&quot;barColor&quot;: &quot;#353535&quot;, &quot;delay&quot;: 900}"><strong>HTML/CSS</strong> <label><span class="percent">85</span>%</label></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<section class="parallax section section-parallax section-center" style="background-image: url(''/adminclanek/img/parallax-transparent.jpg'');" data-stellar-background-ratio="0.5">\r\n<div class="container">\r\n<div class="row">\r\n<div class="col-md-12">\r\n<div class="owl-carousel owl-theme nav-bottom rounded-nav mt-lg mb-none" data-plugin-options="{&quot;items&quot;: 1, &quot;loop&quot;: false}">\r\n<div>\r\n<div class="col-md-12">\r\n<div class="testimonial testimonial-style-6 testimonial-with-quotes mb-none">\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<p>Ctibor mi velmi pomohl s propagac&iacute; m&eacute;ho arboreta i na webov&eacute;m prostoru. Splnil můj hlavn&iacute; požadavek na webdesign : přenesen&iacute; kr&aacute;sy 